	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Whenever I've needed to know what PPU events happen at which PPU cycle, I look at Nintendulator's source code first.  Its PPU source code is arranged so that you can very clearly tell which cycle the scroll increments at, which cycles have memory accesses, etc.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


