		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I would look at Sega Li/FCEU/Nintendulator/LoopyNES (/there's another I forget written entirely in assembly for Win32!) which are all light emulators and mostly straight forward. I worked on an emulator that would have been great for this because it was &lt;1000 lines of C, but I delete things out of perfectionism :)

		

		</td>
